{"tid":1924371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博：特朗普將於當地時間星期五下午三點召開記者會 宣布全國進入緊急狀態！","createTime":"2020-03-13T15:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T16:42:18.000Z","uid":63113,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2d3d66ee718de4f0a0bed60b408c3d82508dbaf0","tid":1924371,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0602b7b2332a2d42107563e87af8b08b5799d9d","tid":1924371,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐全球，《彭博》引述消息報道，美國總統特朗普計劃，星期五宣布進入國家緊急狀態，加強應對武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》的報道指，特朗普將會在當地時間下午 3 點開記者會，預料可以會公布這決定；而近期隨著疫情加劇，民主黨一直在參議院向特朗普施壓，要求他頒布緊急狀態令，以動用多達 420 億美元（約 3276 億港元）的賑災基金應對疫情；一旦宣布進入國家緊急狀態，各州政府可以向聯邦政府申請，分擔 75％ 應急費用，包括醫療測試、物資、疫苗等開支。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E4%BA%94%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83-%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%258D%259A-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%259C%259F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583-%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E7%258B%2580%25E6%2585%258B%2F&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=5e20b653\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%258D%259A-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%259C%259F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583-%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6